.B txt2ss 
\- generate a nicely formatted slipsheet pdf from plain text
.br
.B watch-ibuild 
\- wait for an Ipro build to complete
.br
.B watch-icommit 
\- wait for an Ipro commit to complete
.br
.B watch-iexport 
\- wait for an Ipro ecap export to complete
.br
